description: [``botocore``] This release adds JobStateTimeLimitActions setting to the Job Queue API. It allows you to configure an action Batch can take for a blocking job in front of the queue after the defined period of time. The new parameter applies for ECS, EKS, and FARGATE Job Queues.
[``botocore``] Documentation update for Bedrock Runtime Agent
[``botocore``] Added exceptions to CreateTrail, DescribeTrails, and ListImportFailures APIs.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for a new webhook event: PULL_REQUEST_CLOSED.
[``botocore``] Add RDS Provisioned and Serverless Usage types
[``botocore``] Added DES_EDE3_CBC to the list of supported encryption algorithms for messages sent with an AS2 connector.
